{
  "text": "Is it as efficacious to cleanse the house with salt and water after we move in as it is to do it prior to… we move in? I am Ra. In this case it is not an urgent metaphysical concern as timing would be in a less benign and happy atmosphere. One notes the relative simplicity of accomplishing such prior to occupancy. This is unimportant except as regards the catalyst with which you wish to deal.",
